## 📖 Overview

**TradeWise Pro** is a professional-grade stock trading simulator that allows users to practice trading with real-time market data. The platform supports multiple markets including US stocks, Hong Kong stocks, and A-shares, with integrated AI analysis powered by DeepSeek.

### ✨ Key Features

- 📊 **Real-time Stock Quotes** - Live data via Finnhub API
- 🔍 **Stock Search** - Search by symbol or company name
- 📈 **Watchlist Management** - Add/remove stocks to your personal watchlist
- 💰 **Paper Trading** - Practice trading with $100,000 virtual capital
- 📊 **Portfolio Tracking** - Real-time P&L calculation
- 🤖 **AI Trading Assistant** - Powered by DeepSeek AI for market analysis
- ☁️ **GitHub Sync** - Save your trading strategies to GitHub
- 📱 **Responsive Design** - Works on desktop and tablet devices

---

## ⚠️ Known Issues

### Candlestick Chart (K-Line) - Under Development

> **Status:** 🚧 Work in Progress

The candlestick chart feature is currently experiencing data fetching issues. When the Finnhub API fails to return data (due to rate limits or network issues), the chart falls back to simulated data.

**What works:**
- ✅ Chart rendering with ECharts
- ✅ Timeframe switching (1D, 1W, 1M, 3M, 1Y)
- ✅ Tooltip with OHLC data

**What needs improvement:**
- ❌ Consistent real-time K-line data from API
- ❌ Historical data accuracy
- ❌ Smooth real-time updates

**Roadmap:**
- [ ] Implement WebSocket for real-time candle updates
- [ ] Add more data sources as fallback (Alpha Vantage, Yahoo Finance)
- [ ] Cache historical data to reduce API calls
- [ ] Add technical indicators (MA, RSI, MACD)

