## 🔧 Installation

### Local Development

1. **Clone the repository**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/tradewise-pro.git
cd tradewise-pro
```

2. **Open the application**
```bash
# Simply open index.html in your browser
open index.html
```

3. **Login with demo account**
```
Username: demo
Password: demo123
```

### API Key Configuration

The application uses the following APIs (keys are already embedded for demo purposes):

| API | Purpose | Free Tier Limit |
|-----|---------|-----------------|
| Finnhub | Stock quotes & candles | 60 requests/min |
| DeepSeek | AI analysis | 200k tokens/month |

