## 📊 API Rate Limits

| API | Limit | Reset |
|-----|-------|-------|
| Finnhub | 60 requests/min | Every minute |
| DeepSeek | 200k tokens/month | Monthly |

When rate limits are exceeded, the app falls back to simulated data.

